{"id":234451,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/06/维权网-成都访民维权「简报」第十四期/","date":"2012-06-25T09:30:59Z","modified":"2012-06-25T09:30:59Z","title":"维权网 | 成都访民维权「简报」第十四期","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>•</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>•</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1_6</span><span>•</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>宗旨：给政府提供维稳线索；留下访民辛酸足迹（冰山一角）。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>，锦江区琉璃乡祝国寺村</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>组强拆访民向永会母女到成都市公安局督察，投诉柳江派出所在她们家被不明身份人员非法强拆她们报警后不及时出警，以及反复报警出警后见不明人员非法强拆房屋不阻止。起初成都市公安局督察不受理，在母女反复哭诉后成都市公安局督察叫来当地派出所，带回当地派出所立房屋被毁案。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日</span><span>，成都锦江区六四遇难者母亲唐德英受到八九名不明人员跟踪。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>、6月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日，成都金牛区强拆访民王贤成，经过几月的上访努力，终于从成都市国土局拿到了金牛区金牛乡</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1997-2010</span><span>土地利用规划图，从该图他发现他们的土地多处被政府违规利用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日</span><span>，青羊区草市街强拆访民廖才俐，从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日</span><span>开始一直由一名街道办安排人员看守至今。敏感时间人员增至四五人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日</span><span>，青羊区强拆访民刘存钦到省监察厅、成都市中级法院、省高院上访。都没有人接待。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>，</span><span></span><span>成都武侯区强拆访民吴明仁诉成都市发改委不作为案，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>在成都市高新区人民法院开庭。李庭惠、王蓉文、周成群、邓品芳等二十多位访民参加旁听。据悉此案</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span>日</span><span>开庭因原告吴明仁、旁听李廷惠不满意法院的违规处置而遭司法拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日的报复。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日</span><span>，周成群、李廷惠、陈伦珍、王蓉文、吴明仁、金玉香、李发清、刘廷芳等九人到成华区法院，询问装饰材料厂的集体赔偿案为何超期</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月不审。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日</span><span>，成都成华区圣灯街建北社区圣灯村</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>组近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">40</span><span>名村民联名给孟建柱、省公安厅、成都市公安局上交上访书。反映</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28-30</span><span>日三天</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>组村民集体财产被非法暴力毁坏一案。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日</span><span>，成都温江区</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">140</span><span>户出租车被侵权案，因</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>•</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>进京上访被截访后回温江被拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span>天的访民被释放。据悉，这次集体上访事件共拘</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>人。拘</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>天的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>人，拘</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>天的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>人，拘</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>天的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>人，拘</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>天的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>人，拘</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span>天的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>人，没去上访而被怀疑组织者刑拘</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>人。外地在温江经营出租车被拘者还受到暴力殴打，并威胁：老子叫你消失就消失。被拘</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>天者出狱还要求交</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5000</span><span>保证金，及保证不上访的保证书。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日</span><span>开始，成都锦江区六四遇难者母亲唐德英由原</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>人一班三班倒看守，变成</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>人一班三班倒。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>，彭艳、董春模、周成群、李廷惠、陈伦珍到省国土资源局土地执法监察总队上访。门卫带领大家到办公室后，无人接待，里边工作人员也没佩戴工作牌。后来他们到省国土资源厅信访处上访，由金处长接待。他态度恶劣，对董春模说：你走遍四川，你的问题也都得不到解决。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>日</span><span>，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">40</span><span>左右刘存钦、彭艳、董春模、周成群、李廷惠、陈伦珍到到高院上访，反映高新区法院压案不审，由詹法官接待。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">35</span><span>他们又到中级人民法院反映违法压案不审问题，由法警曾支队接待，警号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">510203</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>日</span><span>，成都双流学生＂右派”冤民罗开文到锦江区公安分局找到多次向其投诉的戴良警察，讯问他投诉自己被警察殴打几月的调查答复情况，戴警察说，再给他们一月时间调查。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>日</span><span>，因围观刘贤斌案被以“煽动颠覆国家政权罪”被刑拘一个月监视居住半年的锦江区冤民，李仁玉家门口路面又受到随意倒毁改造。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span><span>年一次的倒毁改造其他住户都得到补偿，而她家至今未给予补偿。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日</span><span>，金牛访民陈茜诉四川省司法厅行政不作为一审胜诉后，司法厅不服，上诉至中院。今天在中院</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>法庭开庭审理。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>「遗漏补充」：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日</span><span>，上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>点左右。锦江区琉璃乡祝国寺村</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>组向永会母女遭到不明人员非法控制后，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span><span>多名不明身份人员强拆了她们的房屋。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>、5月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日，青羊区强拆访民刘存钦到省监察厅上访。随后又到区纪委上访，区纪委书记不见，由副书记接待。副书记要求她写一份材料，她</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2003</span><span>年被强拆时被毁坏的东西目录及价值。刘存钦很生气道：我上访快十年了，我为啥上访你们不清楚，我的财产都有手续，你们抢了什么？毁坏了什么？你们给我写个清单。上访不欢而散。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-1128527162392401836?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[9085,16910]}